257
00:15:38,493 --> 00:15:39,326
Huh?!

258
00:15:40,926 --> 00:15:42,626
<i>I didn't think he could</i>
<i>use ninjutsu! When did</i>
<i>he learn that?!</i>

259
00:15:42,893 --> 00:15:44,759
Leaf Revolution!

260
00:15:45,359 --> 00:15:46,826
