261
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:53,493
That's nowhere near
enough wind. Just leave
this to me!

262
00:15:57,459 --> 00:16:00,226
Uh, Naruto,
what is that?

263
00:16:00,259 --> 00:16:03,259
Listen, if you're gonna
snatch someone's purse,
you don't want a sad little
gust of wind, you need-

264
00:16:03,293 --> 00:16:05,493
<i>Please don't try</i>
<i>this at home, kids!</i>

265
00:16:05,526 --> 00:16:09,293
