have my secret backup
plan!

273
00:16:37,026 --> 00:16:37,959
[grunt]

274
00:16:37,993 --> 00:16:40,293
[groaning]

275
00:16:40,326 --> 00:16:44,459
My alarm did not go off!
I will be late for my
first day of school!

276
00:16:44,826 --> 00:16:47,293
