Brow! Keep it up!

277
00:16:49,493 --> 00:16:50,426
[gasp]

278
00:16:51,859 --> 00:16:53,326
[groaning]

279
00:16:53,359 --> 00:16:55,326
Watch where you're
going, would ya?

280
00:16:57,326 --> 00:17:00,626
[bell ringing]

281
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:02,493
[gasp]

282
00:17:02,526 --> 00:17:03,459
Huh!

283
00:17:03,926 --> 00:17:05,459
It's you!
It is you!

284
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:11,559
I call this my, "Crash into
her while eating toast on
the way to the first day of
school, see her in homeroom,

285
00:17:11,593 --> 00:17:14,826
