290
00:17:26,959 --> 00:17:28,293
[groaning]

291
00:17:28,326 --> 00:17:31,526
Ah! I am so sorry!
Are you hurt, ma'am!

292
00:17:34,359 --> 00:17:36,893
Hold on tight! I will
get you to the hospital!

293
00:17:37,993 --> 00:17:41,559
Bushy Brow! You're
killing me here!

294
00:17:41,593 --> 00:17:42,426
[sigh]

295
00:17:42,926 --> 00:17:44,659
This is getting
us nowhere.

296
00:17:44,693 --> 00:17:49,693
And we're getting there
fast! Alls we've done is
put her on guard even
more! At this rate,

297
00:17:49,726 --> 00:17:52,393
she won't want to open
her handbag ever again!

298
00:17:52,426 --> 00:17:53,693
Open her handbag...

299
00:17:53,726 --> 00:17:55,359
That is it, Naruto!

300
00:17:55,393 --> 00:17:55,993
Huh?

301
00:17:56,326 --> 00:17:57,759
We will have
her open it!

302
00:17:58,026 --> 00:17:58,959
What?

303
00:18:01,559 --> 00:18:02,959
Hey, Haruno!

304
00:18:02,993 --> 00:18:03,659
Huh?

305
00:18:04,826 --> 00:18:07,326
Stop! We must
inspect your bag!

306
00:18:07,626 --> 00:18:10,859
What?! Hold on!
Who are you guys?

307
00:18:10,893 --> 00:18:15,826
Guidance counselors sent
to put a stop to any
behavior that is unbecoming
of a ninja from our village.

308
00:18:15,859 --> 00:18:17,959
No, I mean...
Guidance ninja!

309
00:18:17,993 --> 00:18:20,259
What the heck's
a guidance ninja?

310
00:18:22,059 --> 00:18:24,493
We just need to take a
look in your bag. We've
had problems with a whole
lot of ninja lately.

311
00:18:24,526 --> 00:18:27,359
Carrying items unrelated
to their mission, ya know.

312
00:18:27,393 --> 00:18:31,793
Uh! What items?!
I'll just have to...
Wing it!

313
00:18:31,826 --> 00:18:33,726
Sorry for the
trouble! Now...

314
00:18:33,759 --> 00:18:34,859
Hey, hold on!

315
00:18:38,459 --> 00:18:40,659
<i>No! It is not</i>
<i>here, Naruto!</i>

316
00:18:40,693 --> 00:18:43,559
C'mon! What're you
doing, Bushy Brow!
Hurry it up!

317
00:18:43,593 --> 00:18:45,393
