may be the only chance
that I ever get to see
them in all their glory!

328
00:19:16,326 --> 00:19:20,559
<i>No! What is wrong with</i>
<i>me?! Naruto would be</i>
<i>disgusted if he knew!</i>

329
00:19:21,426 --> 00:19:25,759
<i>Even with those panties</i>
<i>staring him in the face,</i>
<i>Naruto is focused on that</i>
<i>love letter!</i>

330
00:19:26,626 --> 00:19:29,826
<i>Wait! He is completely</i>
<i>focused on the panties!</i>

331
00:19:29,859 --> 00:19:30,759
<i>Naruto!</i>

332
00:19:30,793 --> 00:19:32,593
