Come to think of it,
she said her stomach
was bothering her.

351
00:20:27,593 --> 00:20:31,559
Never mind that! The plan
was a bust, but now we
have her handbag!

352
00:20:31,593 --> 00:20:33,059
All right...

353
00:20:33,093 --> 00:20:35,426
